=&quot;SkoYn6&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem-component=&quot;productcard:12395424&quot;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;DuxcBA&quot;>;Ace LTE 是一款跨平台产品独立手表；父母或监护人使用 Android 或 iOS 上的 Fitbit Ace 应用程序进行设置。那...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266358/fitbit-ace-lte-kids-smartwatch-amazon-prime-big- Deals-day&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266358/fitbit-ace-lte-kids-smartwatch-amazon-prime-big-deals-day" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266358/fitbit-ace-lte-kids-smartwatch-amazon-prime-big-deals-day</id><author><name>内森·爱德华兹</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T16:13:09-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T16:13:09-04:00</updated><title>您可以在我们最喜欢的一些小工具上获得最佳 Prime Day 优惠</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示时间之轮的回显屏幕&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/fiAUGSYltJ_o2yhwwsxFtpkPOg0=/0x41:922x656/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/ uploads/chorus_image/image/73639601/Screenshot_2024_10_09_at_10.38.01_AM.5.png&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：亚马逊&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;6SIrOL&quot;>;现在是亚马逊 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24255302/amazon-prime-day-deals-tips-news-guide-2024-october&quot;>;十月 Prime Day 活动&lt;/a>;，并且由于该公司仍在推动很多有趣的交易，我们浏览了一些最近的“最爱”文章，找到了许多我们喜欢的设备的折扣。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;SeruAu&quot;>;什么是“最喜欢”的文章？嗯，大约每个月，我们都会询问我们的员工&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/22344288/favorite-gadgets-tech-lgear-aptops-headphones-kitchen-recommendations&quot;>;他们最喜欢的东西东西&lt;/a>;——无论是棋盘游戏、智能科技还是厨房用具。结果通常是古怪的、个性化的，而且很有趣。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;CP4RWK&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem- component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;亚马逊 10 月 Prime Day 促销的最佳优惠&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge. com/good-deals/24262468/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sales-tech-gadgets-october-2024&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;如何在亚马逊秋季 Prime Day 促销期间找到最优惠的价格&quot;, &quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/21502865/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-how-to-find&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;您可以获得的最佳 10 月 Prime Day 优惠低于 100 美元&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24264356/amazon-prime-day-best-cheap-tech-deals-under-100-october-2024&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt; /div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;Cl5ECB&quot;>;所以，我们认为我们应该列出一些，以防您过去读过它们并认为，嗯，这听起来不错，但有点贵。 （或者 - 这相当便宜，但也许我会等到价格进一步下降...）&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;2O3Ixo&quot;>;以下是我们的一些员工的...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24265074/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sale-tech-staff-picks-favorites-october-2024&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/一个>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/24265074/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sale-tech-staff-picks-favorites-october-2024" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/24265074/amazon-prime-day-best-deals-sale-tech-staff-picks-favorites-october-2024</id><author><name>芭芭拉·克拉斯诺夫</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T16:10:36-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T16:10:36-04:00</updated><title> Instagram 和 Threads 的审核失控</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;显示 Threads 徽标的图像&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/iwRS5EimuNlJ-liEHU2hzd-qimw=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn .com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73643063/STK156_Instagram_threads_3.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：边缘&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;33gNdo&quot;>;在线程上，“线程”的主题审核失败”&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.threads.net/search?q=Threads%20Moderation%20Failures&quot;>;正在流行&lt;/a>;。一些用户抱怨他们的帐户因链接到有争议主题的文章而被删除或限制。 Instagram 和 Threads 老板 Adam Mosseri &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.threads.net/@mosseri/post/DA4aJFvvxTc&quot;>;直接回复&lt;/a>;一些投诉和&lt;a href=&quot;https://www .threads.net/@mosseri/post/DA55gP6xqMb?xmt=AQGztKVi-d95TvnowJ6kiTgIeYsxiCz_Rf5vansejAiL4Q&quot;>;说&lt;/a>;他正在“调查此事”。我是&lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/Ricky_Babcock/status/1843684704182231322&quot;>;其中一个&lt;/a>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/IamGabeG/status/1843381623288742394&quot;>; &lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/Tiernan_Avery21/status/1843695744567652402&quot;>;很多&lt;/a>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://x.com/8BitShowAndTell/status/1842743495108538454&quot;>;人&lt;/a>; 谁的帐户因涉嫌是儿童而被删除 - 但我不是。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;HMzBf7&quot;>;审核是社交媒体上长期存在的问题，但基于社交媒体帖子和 &lt;em >;The Verge&lt;/em>; 工作人员的亲身经历，Meta 目前正在一触即发地禁止和限制用户。我的一位同事本周&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.threads.net/@kylie.robison/post/DA3i2qIPY8v&quot;>;她的帐户被短暂锁定&lt;/a>;&lt;a href=&quot;https:// /www.threads.net/@kylie.robison/post/DAzGBjjzFNG&quot;>;开玩笑&lt;/a>;之后，她因为热浪而“想死”。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c -float-hang&quot;>;&lt;div id=&quot;ks1uU2&quot;>; &lt;div class=&quot;iframely-embed&quot;>;&lt;div class=&quot;iframely-responsive&quot; style=&quot;padding-bottom: 100%;&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot; https://www.threads.net/@mosseri/post/DA55gP6xqMb&quot; data-iframely-url=&quot;https://cdn.iframe.ly/api/iframe?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads。 net%2F%40mosseri%2Fpost%2FDA55gP6xqMb&amp;amp;key=9ef4a209439e42bc59783ba959d50197&quot;>;&lt;/a>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;/div>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;XUK76q&quot;>;其他，如 Jorge... &lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266096/instagram-threads-moderation-account-post-deleted-limited&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/一个>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266096/instagram-threads-moderation-account-post-deleted-limited" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/9/24266096/instagram-threads-moderation-account-post-deleted-limited</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-09T16:02:09-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-09T16:02:09-04:00</updated><title>关于任天堂闹钟的所有讨论</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;任天堂 Alarmo 闹钟的照片。&qu